org.apache.commons.rdf.api

Interface TripleOrQuad

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Quad, Triple

    public interface TripleOrQuad
    Common "triple-like" interface for Triple and Quad

    A TripleOrQuad has at least a getSubject(), getPredicate() and getObject(), but unlike a Triple does not have a formalised Triple.equals(Object) semantics, and does not necessarily have a Quad.getGraphName()

    Implementations of this interface SHOULD also implement Triple or Quad, but MUST NOT implement both interfaces.

    • Method Summary
